Package: sfXtra
Type: Package
Title: Advanced sf functions
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(
	person("Tayo", "Ososanya", email = "tayo.ososanya@arcadisgen.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	person("David", "Smith", email = "david.smith@arcadisgen.com", role = c("aut"))
	)
Description: The sfXtra family was created to solve advanced sf problems. This includes get elevation, 
    find nearest, convert coordinates, break_linestrings, distance calculator etc. Feel free to raise an issue you face 
	using this package. Also, you can add your friendly geo-spatial functions to make this library more robust.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.1)
